  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>\u2212</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>r</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>\u2212</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>The equation above is true for all <math><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>3</mn></math>, where <em>r</em> and <em>t</em> are constants. What is the value of <em>rt</em>?</p>",
